55, 255)">01</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">月</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">24</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">日上午</span></span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">11</span><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">：</span>00开启首次删档测试。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">本次测试中开放了几十位传说级英雄、酷炫主城、瑰丽场景、经典战场、霸气坐骑、</span>Q萌宠物等，在游戏肿可以体验到冒险副本、野外战斗、角斗场、竞技场、试炼等特色玩法。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">本次测试为删档测试，服务器开始时间为：</span>5月24日上午11:00，在此之前请耐心等。</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(255, 136, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:微软雅黑">正式上线后将陆续开放更多新英雄、坐骑、宠物、英雄皮肤。大战场多人混战、实时</span>PK、新地图MOBA5V5等也会在后续的版本陆续开放。大家敬请期待！</span></p><p style="text-indent:28px"><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;color: rgb(255, 136, 0);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 14px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">◆&nbsp;当前版本为测试版本，不代表最终游戏品质</span></p><p><br/></p>";s:8:"catelist";a:1:{i:68;a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:2:"68";s:5:"title";s:6:"公告";s:10:"identifier";s:12:"announcement";s:3:"url";s:22:"news/announcement.html";}}s:4:"cate";a:4:{s:7:"cate_id";s:2:"68";s:5:"title";s:6:"公告";s:10:"identifier";s:12:"announcement";s:3:"url";s:22:"news/announcement.html";}s:3:"url";s:9:"1821.html";}}}